node.text:
On the latest episode of #ForumFridays, host @wayno119 sat down with members of the S.E.E.D. Program, Adidas' School for Experiential Education in Design, located at the brand's Brooklyn Creator Farm. Comprised of female creators, the inaugural class, Generation 2020, discusses the future of footwear design, their creative process, and much more.

Hit the link in bio for the full episode!
